metadata.name: Remarkable Women SIS 2023 Tribute NFT
metadata.description:
The Remarkable Women SIS 2023 Tribute NFT commemorates the 2023 Landmark Ventures Social Innovation Summit at the Beverly Hilton in Los Angeles, CA, June 6th-7th. 

SIS is an event platform for a network of social impact leaders across corporate responsibility, philanthropy, investment, technology, and innovation. 
     
Anchored around our Flagship Social Innovation Summit held each June, our top-tier programming, curated networking, and memorable experiences, we catalyze purpose-driven partnerships across Future of Work & Education, Health & Wellness, Tech for Good, ESG & Corporate Leadership, Economic Empowerment, Social Justice & DEI, Philanthropy Environment & Sustainability, and more. 

The Remarkable Women NFT Collection is a collaboration between the House of First and artist Rachel Winter.
